Culinary Adventures

Overview

Culinary Adventures is an innovative recipe app designed to inspire users to step out of their culinary comfort zones. This app offers a unique and fun approach to cooking by encouraging creativity and exploration in the kitchen.

Features

1. Ingredient Explorer:
   - Enter an ingredient and receive a photo of a meal you can try to recreate without a recipe. This feature sparks creativity and improvisation in the kitchen.

2. Meal Name Challenge:
   - Input the name of a meal, view a photo, and attempt to recreate it from scratch. This feature helps hone your cooking skills through experimentation and discovery.

3. Random Recipe:
   - Click the random recipe button and follow detailed instructions to create a new and unique dish. This feature expands your culinary repertoire with guided exploration.

Built With

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- React
- Redux Toolkit

Hosted On

- Netlify

Getting Started

Prerequisites

- Node.js
- npm (Node Package Manager)

Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/culinary-adventures.git
   cd culinary-adventures
   ```

2. Install the dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. Start the development server:
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```

4. Open your browser and navigate to `http://localhost:3000`.

